{
  "stem": "10862.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And the men, I didn't see.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "The men were completely taken away in another section of the camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And when the German told me to throw the child down, he also told me to run.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I don't know what made this German soldier to tell me to run.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "For that split second maybe I reminded him either of his own child.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Maybe I reminded him of a grandchild because I was a blond little girl.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I don't know what made him do those things, but he told me to run, and I ran into the pile of the dirty clothes where the women had just taken off all their clothing.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And as I was laying in the dirty pile of clothes, the same German soldier that had a little bit of pity for a split second, a little bit of humanity in him for that split second, took out a gun and shot all the 11 children right in front of me while I was laying in, in that dirty pile of clothes.",
      "word_count": 63
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "There was an open pit and he just with a machine gun went boom, boom, boom, boom like this and he-- that was the end of all the kids.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then finally when it came dark I ran into the barrack where the women were going in, and as I came into the barrack all the women started attacking me, asking me all sorts of questions.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Where are the children?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Where-- what happened to the children?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What happened to the children?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And, of course, my sisters were just overwhelmed with happiness and tears when they saw me because they too thought that I was going to be killed.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Somehow or another I had enough sense not to say anything.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
